title: Yahoo Lifestyle
text: Youre seeking to reignite your excitement for a once-prized possession by buying something else thats new and shiny. This sense of urgency might prompt you to spend money quickly on anything that proves as fleeting in its value as the last object of your affection. Although the ever-changing Taurus Moon conspires with uncontainable Uranus in your 2nd House of Possessions, the true source of any thrill doesnt rest in the material world. Your joy is the special ingredient in everything you touch. Get Your Complete Cosmic Profile
